    <p>{`If you haven’t heard of SOPA/PIPA by now, you obviously don’t use the internet– in which case neither of them are likely of huge concern to you. But if you do use the internet and have just been avoiding learning about the two US Congress bills (house/senate respectively) check out this informative video. After the leap, read my opinion about the bills, the internet blackout, ‘Silicon Valley vs. Hollywood’, and other general comments.`}</p>
    <div {...{
      "className": "gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper",
      "style": {
